{
  "stem": "23572.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like-- Like-- You've heard the expression, 'the quislings,' the collaborators-- these were the Croatian Nazis.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "P-A-V-L-E-I-C-H, Pavelic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that was his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, he was-- he got-- I understand, after the war, they hanged him with all the rest of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Real-- real-- Yeah, real-- real Nazis, probably thugs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what kind of a doctor he was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we were there in this-- in this in the Jewish community in Leipzig-- I mean, in Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were-- in the meantime, I met other children who arrived later from Germany-- Berlin, Frankfurt, you name it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just remember there was one girl from Leipzig.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was-- they were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were finally together in the Jewish Community Center.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we started to organize ourselves into a group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We found one man who was-- he was a Yugoslavian Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Thank God he's still alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name is-- it was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Today's it's Josef Itaj.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He lives in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was one of the leaders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then we had some other-- some other people-- a fellow by the name of Marko Silberschaltz who died, a great fellow by the name of Dr.-- Professor Boris Jochvidson.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was from Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so we-- we decided to organize ourselves and figured we have to do something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the meantime, the-- the-- the decree came out that all Jews have to wear the badge, a yellow badge with a 'z' on it, which means [?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Zidov. ?] OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Zidov. ?] And I remember one instance where, first of all, I went to the-- we went to the German-- to the German army headquarters.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were figuring, we were Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were German citizens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "See the army, the army was not the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
